			<h3 class="heading-<?php echo $gPageColor; ?>"><strong>Markets and Food Trucks</strong></h3>
			<p>San Francisco has a ton of food markets to explore and the food truck culture is also very strong. Be sure to check some out for cheap, fresh, and innovative food.</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a class="body-link" href="https://www.ferrybuildingmarketplace.com/" target="_blank">Ferry Building</a> &mdash; San Francisco's main ferry terminal is also a massive food hall, and on Saturday mornings is the site of an enormous farmers' market, one of our favourites in the city</li>
				<li><a class="body-link" href="https://agriculturalinstitute.org/directory/listing-details/clement-st" target="_blank">Clement St Farmers' Market</a> &mdash; Our local farmers' market that runs every Sunday morning and located just three blocks from our apartment</li>
