				<li><a class="body-link" href="https://offthegrid.com/" target="_blank">Off the Grid</a> &mdash; A series of food truck festivals located throughout the city, our favourites are the Presidio Picnic on Sundays on the Main Post lawn and the one at Fort Mason on Fridays...but check the website for full details of the 2018 season starting in April</li>
